						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Tuḷajarāja Saheb Year: 10, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription begins with an obeisance to the God Bhavāni Śankara. Records the consecration of the temple (Dēvāli) by Du(Tu)lajā rāja, Mahārājā sāḥeb Rāmaji rāje sāheb. The date portion is not clear, probably mentions a cyclic year and 10th Monday.</p>						

						</summary>
